The #Packers are currently 5 point underdogs at home vs. the #Cowboys. It's the first time in Aaron Rodgers' career as a starting QB!
#nflverse https://t.co/8Agu9FJu1J
Trying to refresh my Python skills and play around with play by play data. Thanks @_TanHo for the data on #nflverse https://t.co/jvZit0JGYZ

For those who prefer the #NFL, here are every team's 𝗲𝗳𝗳𝗶𝗰𝗶𝗲𝗻𝗰𝘆 𝗿𝗮𝘁𝗶𝗻𝗴𝘀 for each week of the season so far.

Better performing teams will have more points top-right ↗️ of their panel.

Season averages are below team names.

#nflverse https://t.co/IwgNaMhyeP

Pillboxes, people!! Here's KC offense on a 100 total offensive snaps game!! Toney got 8 of 9 snaps on 1st or 2nd downs. Pacheco started again, then McKinnon took over. Skyy stayed involved the entire game, as did Justin Watson. 

#nflverse #rstats https://t.co/xBeujPxrCc

Chiefs defense. Sneed and McDuffie played nearly every snap. We were in base a lot, so didn't have a third CB on the field for those snaps. Williams played over Watson, though, when a 3rd CB was required. Wonder if that split will be matchup dependent.

#nflverse #rstats https://t.co/VXGs5P3KiU

Happy Snaps by Formations day!! Here’s KC’s 99(!!) offensive snaps, on a day we got 499 net yards of offense and it felt like we got 229 instead. As a note, Pats (magnificent) scrambles count as pass plays, since they were dropbacks, not designed scrambles. 

#nflverse #rstats https://t.co/NllTMclqJs
